390
00:13:50,625 --> 00:13:53,041
Oh, come on, Charlotte.
I apologized for saying that.

391
00:13:53,083 --> 00:13:54,750
No, you've been talking to me
like you've apologized.

392
00:13:54,792 --> 00:13:56,417
You've been saying
the things people say

