get her a job?

493
00:17:33,583 --> 00:17:35,417
That's not really the way
the process works.

494
00:17:35,458 --> 00:17:37,500
I just... I don't know.

495
00:17:37,542 --> 00:17:39,625
If I induce her, then i'm
gonna feel responsible for

496
00:17:39,667 --> 00:17:41,625
